nodes.text: Peter Moore directed the audio dramatization of Crimson Empire. He also provided some of the voices for the same audio drama.

He voiced Slyder in Dark Forces: Soldier for the Empire audio drama; Nij Por Ral and 8t88 in Dark Forces: Rebel Agent audio drama; and an unnamed officer and a Floater in Dark Forces: Jedi Knight audio drama.
